{"tid":505630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有試過俾同性朋友鍾意過嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-12-21T10:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T05:15:25.000Z","uid":159904,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"64bb5212f6b6e07610eaaa35121090d2dec7c21e","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"話說有個同性朋友早排好突然咁話鍾意咗我<br />\n其實有少許意外<br />\n因為我地識左好耐<br />\n我地做朋友嗰陣<br />\n但佢好鍾意無啦啦攬實我<br />\n會突然拖住我隻手<br />\n如果有其他男仔接近我 <br />\n佢又會唔鍾意<br />\n咁大個女第一次俾女仔表白<br />\n我真係唔知點面對佢<br />\n所以佢表白後一直都無點理到佢<br />\n佢約親我去街 <br />\n我都一定會拒絕<br />\n其實佢好希望同我好似以前咁<br />\n但我又好抗拒佢咁親密咁對我<br />\n成日&quot;形&quot;住&quot;形&quot;住咁<br />\n個感覺好奇怪<br />\n平時佢做呢啲野我都無乜野<br />\n但自從知道佢鍾意我<br />\n我就表現得好抗拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔想咁做㗎<br />\n但我控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論佢做啲咩我都覺得好唔舒服<br />\n唔想我地好似以前咁close<br />\n但又唔想大家連朋友都無得做<br />\n唉我都唔知自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該點做好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申有同過男仔拍拖 我100%係鍾意男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a7fcf603ef89f8636fc116773b0e3f617d12a7","tid":505630,"uid":104502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"唔想就遠離人啦"},{"pid":"6059ec1fe81b879f1e2aae43933a5f722c907ee3","tid":505630,"uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"試過返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"dddd864a9af52062de3361746c42d2fac87efce1","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想就遠離人啦</blockquote><br />\n點樣遠離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一堆人玩埋一齊<br />\n當中有佢有我<br />\n入面啲人全部唔知佢鍾意我<br />\n因為我唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係講咗俾幾個唔係嗰堆嘅朋友知咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc88040ff39c3c9bc1c914c4fafa9858843ade6","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過返唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打你嘅情況係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾有冇做返朋友<br />\n你點樣面對返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5399db5227e8ec8e3fad9a48fa83c6f7f53e0095","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"我唔係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n100%真人真事<br />\n想搵各位連登仔俾下意見<br />\n點解要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0851b08132af83ce236d8ad9c316daa98953ea","tid":505630,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:36:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfc8e14750ce55f3220fe3636e407521cb7826fa","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講清楚，不過都係會冇咗個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢以前對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋係好好嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要做到咁絕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cafa183598caf3a9f39e5ecf040cbb1367207a","tid":505630,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:41:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd732cd1a003490b83f560013b4967784390211","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你對住佢個陣有條刺,<br />\n咁樣又好咩?<br />\n<br />\n唔能夠全心全意做好朋友只能夠做陌路人</blockquote><br />\n我應該點樣表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次遇到呢種情況唔知點樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8b9cfdf69274042ff266139f345a8922326faf","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2fc7f49d9ff221dd37ec3d53d4b990c426f6da","tid":505630,"uid":30442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"同佢講清楚<br />\n之後就當佢係男性朋咁相處"},{"pid":"06805afe966e1bd44a04b5701642b953b4b07b49","tid":505630,"uid":122619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"你咪同佢保持返距離 一大班fd出嚟玩咪避免同佢接觸<br />\n最緊要同佢講清楚你自己睇法 唔好覺得唔好意思唔講<br />\n寧願少左個朋友都唔好俾假幻想人 做好自己就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5fd23c195196b6ef50ea7a7afd60161f0c86ed","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講清楚<br />\n之後就當佢係男性朋咁相處</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男仔點同女仔喎"},{"pid":"8dc4e90152eedeaf134eddf9dbaf14988afff6fe","tid":505630,"uid":159904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:36:52.000